channel.title: I need help with my rsps! .. /: - Willing to give RS acc for help!
channel.description:
Hey everyone, i need help with my RSPS, i'm trying to make a 562 rsps server, i've choose "Atomic-Scape" as my server, i can get it up to run, my problem is:
1. I need help to change the name, so it's not named Atomic Scape..
2. I need to get it online, ( a big problem! :P )
I basicly just need nearly everything, just not to make it run, becuase i've done that, but i'm a bit alone..
Can you please help me!?.. I got skype & Facebook, and teamviewer..! pm me, if u wanna help me!
- PKAR
